casebody.data:
No. 10-925. Grand Trunk Western Railroad, Inc., Petitioner v. William E. Shepard. 564 U.S. 1053, 131 S. Ct. 3090,

180 L. Ed. 2d 913,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5004. June 28, 2011.

Motion of Association of American Railroads for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Ohio, Cuyahoga County, denied.
